'''Victor Hugo''' d amyaru afransis,  ilul di Besançon ass n 26 di furar 1802, yemmut di [[Paris]] ass n 22 mayu 1885. Yella d anaggal, d amedyaz, d amsezgan am akken yekcem daɣen deg tudert tasertant d tmeɣnest.

Yettuneḥsab d yiwen seg imyura imeqqranen maḍi n tutlayt tafransist, yettwassen ladɣa s wungal-is mucaεen di ddunit « Imeɣban » (les Misérables) i yesseẓreg deg usegass n 1862. Γer tama n tira yelha-d d waṭas n lecɣal-iḍen izuyaz am umennuɣ ɣef yizerfan n wemdam, tugart ayen yerzan tafgurt s tmettant (peine de mort).

